<fdroid>
  <application id="com.nova.ai">
    <name>Nova AI</name>
    <summary>Privacy-focused AI chat with tool calling and web search</summary>
    <desc>Nova AI — Multi-provider support with saved provider profiles, models.dev browser, and OpenCode Zen free models.

Features:
* Save multiple providers and switch between them instantly
* Each provider remembers its API key, model list, and selected model
* Browse 80+ OpenAI-compatible providers from models.dev
* Fetch available models from any provider
* Free models work without an API key (OpenCode Zen)
* Streaming with reasoning/thinking display
* Tool calling: calculator, time, web search (SearXNG)
* Image vision
* Clean bottom sheet UI
* Markdown with tables, code blocks, lists
* No tracking, no ads, no proprietary SDKs
</desc>
